  "detailed_description": "<h1>COMING SOON ! Wishlist now.</h1><p></p><br><h1>MY NEW GAMES</h1><p><br><br><br><br></p><br><h1>MORE 3DM LIVE WALLPAPERS</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>3DM Space Collection</h1><p><br><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Software</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Our latest project Fluid Engine presents a beautiful fluid simulation that responds to your mouse. In options, you can change many parameters that change the appearance and behaviour of the fluid. We have prepared some ready settings for you but you can also add your own (presets) to quickly change them. By default, for 3DM you can also add your own text, logos or clock.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></h2>Interactive simulation - Fluid that reacts to the mouse movement and clicking.<br>Ready presets - a few presets made by us but you can add your own.<br>Many editing options - you can change many parameters.<br>Clock - adjust your clock to the screen.<br>Own text - add your own text to the wallpaper.<br>Own logo - add your own logotype (.PNG, .JPG)<br>Autorun - Starts with Windows 10/11.<br>Automatic and manual Pause Mode - will pause wallpaper when you need 100% power for your games. Will detect full-screen games.<br>Optimization - reduced equipment requirements. Optimized code created for mobile devices.<br>Multi-Language - the menu with many languages.<br><br><strong>The project will be developed so there will probably be more options soon.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Support:</strong><br>We are a tiny team creating interactive 3D wallpapers for Windows 10/11. We try to make each project unique, introducing something new on the screen. Each support is valuable for us. Constructive comments allow us to create even better projects. Any problem? Write to me and I will help.<br><br><strong>Thank you for every support.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Peace</h2>3DM<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/aab8e88c8e6ed58ece70cb6747378249.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Our latest project Fluid Engine presents a beautiful fluid simulation that responds to your mouse. In options, you can change many parameters that change the appearance and behaviour of the fluid. We have prepared some ready settings for you but you can also add your own (presets) to quickly change them. By default, for 3DM you can also add your own text, logos or clock.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></h2>Interactive simulation - Fluid that reacts to the mouse movement and clicking.<br>Ready presets - a few presets made by us but you can add your own.<br>Many editing options - you can change many parameters.<br>Clock - adjust your clock to the screen.<br>Own text - add your own text to the wallpaper.<br>Own logo - add your own logotype (.PNG, .JPG)<br>Autorun - Starts with Windows 10/11.<br>Automatic and manual Pause Mode - will pause wallpaper when you need 100% power for your games. Will detect full-screen games.<br>Optimization - reduced equipment requirements. Optimized code created for mobile devices.<br>Multi-Language - the menu with many languages.<br><br><strong>The project will be developed so there will probably be more options soon.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/cf5e9d5ab3b2ee755a137ba149f2bffa.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Support:</strong><br>We are a tiny team creating interactive 3D wallpapers for Windows 10/11. We try to make each project unique, introducing something new on the screen. Each support is valuable for us. Constructive comments allow us to create even better projects. Any problem? Write to me and I will help.<br><br><strong>Thank you for every support.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Peace</h2>3DM<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.poster.avif?t=1667662740\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.webm?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268040/extras/595cff8a798868b5d9e48c9491973d55.mp4?t=1667662740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
